OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780150315
OL,3,CMemorial unveiled for fans who died at
OL,4,CHeysel Stadium 41 years ago
OL,6,FLiverpool FC has unveiled a new
OL,7,Fmemorial at Anfield to mark the 41st
OL,8,Fanniversary of the Heysel Stadium
OL,9,Fdisaster - honouring the 39 football
OL,10,Fsupporters who lost their lives.
OL,12,FRepresentatives of Serie A club
OL,13,FJuventus were present to see the new
OL,14,F'Forever Bound' sculpture, which
OL,15,Ffeatures two scarves knotted together
OL,16,Fand includes the names of all those
OL,17,Fwho died at the 1985 European Cup
OL,18,Ffinal between the two clubs in
OL,19,FBelgium, when a wall collapsed inside
OL,20,Fthe stadium after rival fans clashed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
