PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780150315
OL,3,CMemorial unveiled for fans who died at
OL,4,CHeysel Stadium 41 years ago
OL,6,FThe stone sculpture now stands in a
OL,7,Fnewly designated area of Anfield,
OL,8,Flocated by the Anfield Road Stand,
OL,9,Fproviding a more visible and
OL,10,Faccessible space for reflection and
OL,11,Fremembrance of the disaster which
OL,12,Fhappened on 29 May 1985.
OL,14,FThe memorial, which was first
OL,15,Fannounced at a special event at
OL,16,FAnfield back in May 2025, replaces the
OL,17,Foriginal plaque located on the wall of
OL,18,Fthe Sir Kenny Dalglish Stand.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
