OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780150315
OL,3,CMemorial unveiled for fans who died at
OL,4,CHeysel Stadium 41 years ago
OL,6,F"It is with a deep sense of respect
OL,7,Fthat we stand together to reflect,
OL,8,Fremember and reaffirm our commitment
OL,9,Fto those we sadly lost that day," said
OL,10,FLiverpool Chief Executive Billy Hogan
OL,11,Fas he stressed the importance of
OL,12,Fremembering the victims.
OL,14,F"We know that remembrance matters and
OL,15,Fit is important for us as a club, our
OL,16,Fstaff, our fans and the wider football
OL,17,Fcommunity that we ensure Heysel is not
OL,18,Fforgotten.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@aO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
