FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780150315
OL,3,CMemorial unveiled for fans who died at
OL,4,CHeysel Stadium 41 years ago
OL,6,F"There is a tremendous amount of
OL,7,Frespect for Juventus football club, as
OL,8,Fan institution and a club, and there
OL,9,Fis a very strong relationship between
OL,10,Fthe two clubs.
OL,12,F"We are grateful to everyone who
OL,13,Fplayed a part in bringing us to
OL,14,Ftoday's unveiling.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
