OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780150315
OL,3,CMemorial unveiled for fans who died at
OL,4,CHeysel Stadium 41 years ago
OL,6,F"It's a beautiful memorial which
OL,7,Fprovides our fans and fans of other
OL,8,Fclubs with a place to come and show
OL,9,Ftheir respect and remember those lives
OL,10,Fthat were lost, and to ensure that
OL,11,Fsomething like that never happens
OL,12,Fagain.
OL,14,F"Let's continue to work forward,
OL,15,Fforever bound, in a mutual respect and
OL,16,Fa shared grief."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUxD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
