PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780150315
OL,3,CMemorial unveiled for fans who died at
OL,4,CHeysel Stadium 41 years ago
OL,6,FThe sculpture has been crafted from
OL,7,Fspecially selected materials,
OL,8,Fincluding Cararra marble sourced from
OL,9,Fan Italian quarry and includes the
OL,10,Fnames of all 39 supporters who lost
OL,11,Ftheir lives and a moving inscription.
OL,13,FIt was created in response to calls
OL,14,Ffrom fans to make the memorial more
OL,15,Fprominent and accessible, and it was
OL,16,Fdeveloped in close consultation with
OL,17,Fsupporters, in particular Spirit of
OL,18,FShankly, and former players.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780150315
OL,3,CMemorial unveiled for fans who died at
OL,4,CHeysel Stadium 41 years ago
OL,6,FPlans were also shared with Juventus
OL,7,FFC and those involved in the original
OL,8,Fcommemorations to ensure the approach
OL,9,Freflected a spirit of unity and shared
OL,10,Flegacy.
OL,12,FLiverpool ambassador Ian Rush, who
OL,13,Fplayed in the 1985 European Cup final
OL,14,Fand witnessed the events of that day,
OL,15,Fadded: "Today is a deeply moving
OL,16,Fmoment.
OL,18,F"It's hard to believe over 40 years
OL,19,Fhave passed since Heysel, but the
OL,20,Fmemory of that day never fades.
OL,26,@wD@HOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
