OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780150315
OL,3,CMemorial unveiled for fans who died at
OL,4,CHeysel Stadium 41 years ago
OL,6,F"This new memorial means a great deal
OL,7,Fto all of us. The thought and respect
OL,8,Fthat has gone into 'Forever Bound' is
OL,9,Fsomething I'm incredibly proud of and
OL,10,FI hope it brings comfort to those
OL,11,Fstill affected by this tragedy."
OL,13,FThe event closed with a moment of
OL,14,Fsilence and floral wreaths were laid
OL,15,Fat the base of the memorial by
OL,16,Frepresentatives from LFC, Juventus and
OL,17,Fthe city of Liverpool. Attendees were
OL,18,Fthen invited to view the sculpture up
OL,19,Fclose and spend time in quiet
OL,20,Freflection.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
